                n="23"
                xml:id="pb-23"
                facs="#i23"/>
            <lb/>
21<lb/>
appears, and disappears, with the flash.<lb/>
This smoke appeared to me<lb/>
extraneous to the lava; at least the<lb/>
fragments of the later <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">neither</hi> smoke,<lb/>
