            <lb/>
themselves in their unexpected delicacies<lb/>
and filling their Boat with them |_ they<lb/>
were suddenly awakened to a sense of<lb/>
danger by a motion of the rocks<lb/>
so voilent, as to throw some of them<lb/>
off their legs" and the little Island<lb/>
suddenly began <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">to rise</hi> and to elevate<lb/>
it self beneath them. - And they<lb/>
