                rend="underline">feet</hi> above<lb/>
the sides of the bason. |_ by a suprise<lb/>
of this kind, while we were engaged <add xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0">in</add>
            <lb/>
measuring the diameter of the well,<lb/>
