we were able to withdraw ourselves from<lb/>
the great body of water as it descended<lb/>
yet we remained exposed to the falling<lb/>
spray, which fortunately was so much<lb/>
cooled in the air as to do us no mischief<lb/>
|_ Of these jets we counted twenty in<lb/>
an hour and half, <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">during which</hi> the waters<lb/>
